      <title>美联储鲍曼：支持12月降息作为“最后”调整步骤</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/feds-bowman-supported-dec-rate-cut-final-recalibration-step-2025-01-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事米歇尔鲍曼周四表示，她支持上个月的降息，认为这是美国央行货币政策重新调整的“最后一步”，通胀风险上升要求未来采取谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/feds-bowman-supported-dec-rate-cut-final-recalibration-step-2025-01-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 18:38:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
