      <title>美联储施密德称央行利率“接近”中性水平</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/feds-schmid-says-central-bank-near-neutral-interest-rate-level-2025-01-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[堪萨斯城联储行长杰夫·施密德周四表示，美联储不愿再次降息，因为在新的一年里，美联储将面临经济复苏和通胀仍高于 2% 目标的局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/feds-schmid-says-central-bank-near-neutral-interest-rate-level-2025-01-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 18:35:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
